{{Expand section|date=May 2008}}
温州话有一个声调指示词素。表达“这”时，[[量词|量词]]变为入声，浊声母也会清化。例如{{IPA|/le˧˩/}}“有些（人）”变为{{IPA|/l̥e˧˨˧/}}“这些（人）”。<ref name="bao">{{Cite book |last=Bao |first=Zhiming |title=The Structure of Tone |date=1999 |publisher=Oxford University Press |isbn=0-19-511880-4 |location=New York |language=en}}</ref>{{rp|119}}

